fields.description:
Just updated to the latest release (running under Win7), and the File Status tab seems to repeatedly refresh itself whenever its focus changes and/or randomly. As a result, I can select numerous files for committing, then switch to another program (email, browser, whatever), and then as soon as I switch back, my multiple file selection is lost because the whole thing seems to 'refresh' itself. Never had this problem with previous builds, as far as I'm aware.

To reproduce:
 * Go to File Status in sourceTree and select multiple files;
 * Switch to another task;
 * Switch back - file selection is reset
